EN: Part-time jobs provide an additional source of income.

ZH: 她兼职来支付她的学费。
EN: She works part-time to pay for her tuition fees.

ZH: 我正在考虑兼职以增加我的工作经验。
EN: I am considering working part-time to gain more work experience.

