EN: Part-time jobs have flexible working hours.

ZH: 大学生常常兼职来减轻经济负担。
EN: College students often work part-time to alleviate their financial burden.

ZH: 我在周末兼职当一名家教。
EN: I work part-time as a tutor on weekends.

